Module kbaldr2.main
Package kbaldr2.model

Class Customer

java.lang.Object
kbaldr2.model.DataCache
kbaldr2.model.Customer
public class Customer extends DataCache
Represents a Customer, extending the DataCache class. Contains customer-specific data such as name, address, postal code, phone number, and division ID.
